creator: Ornamental Tree
descriptionHtml:
Bonsai Campus helps you get an overview of everything that happens on your university and the university campus. Follow departments that suites your interest and get rid of the eternal searching for events on your university over other social media channels. And above all; never ever miss a lunch lecture or any other important information again.

With Bonsai campus you are available to:

- Discover events all over your campus
- Search for departments on your campus
- Save your credit card info for fast payments.
- See event details including maps and directions.
- See relevant information about your upcoming events.
- Share event information with your friends.
- See all your saved tickets, and use them directly in the app.

The app is currently available in Swedish and English.

title: Orbi

creator: Team Orbi
descriptionHtml:
Orbi helps you get an overview of everything that happens at your university and campus. Follow departments that match your interests and stop the eternal search for uni events all over social media. And above all: never ever miss a free lunch lecture again!

With Orbi you'll be able to:
- Purchase tickets for events at campus
- Discover unions and departments at your campus
- See event details, such as information and directions
- Share events with your friends
- Save your credit card info for fast payments
- Browse all your purchased tickets
- Quickly find your tickets once at the door to the event

The app is currently available in English and Swedish

creator: Team Orbi
descriptionHtml:
Orbi helps you get an overview of everything that happens at your university and campus. Follow departments that match your interests and stop the eternal search for uni events all over social media. And above all: never ever miss a free lunch lecture again!

With Orbi you'll be able to:
- Purchase tickets for events at campus
- Discover unions and departments at your campus
- See event details, such as information and directions
- Share events with your friends
- Save your credit card info for fast payments
- Browse all your purchased tickets
- Quickly find your tickets once at the door to the event

The app is currently available in English and Swedish

creator: Team Orbi
descriptionHtml:
Say goodbye to the hassle of keeping track of student life – Orbi brings everything together in one place! Find discounts, buy and sell textbooks, explore career opportunities, and book tickets to the best events.

Simplify Your Student Life with Orbi:
💰 Discounts – Get exclusive student discounts on your favourite brands.
📚 Books – Save money by buying second-hand textbooks or make extra cash by selling yours.
🚀 Career – Connect with top employers, find internships, and build your future.
💬 Communicate – Chat, collaborate, and connect with fellow students.
🎟️ Events & Tickets – Discover and book tickets for the biggest events on campus and beyond.
🌍 Available in English and Swedish.

Download Orbi now and take control of your student life! 🚀🎉
